OL,3,CPolice hunt gunman after man shot dead
OL,4,Cin car near Euston station
OL,6,FA 26-year-old man was shot dead while
OL,7,Fsitting in a car near Euston station
OL,8,Fin central London on Saturday night,
OL,9,Fthe Metropolitan Police said.
OL,11,FThe man died at the scene in Chalton
OL,12,FStreet despite the efforts of
OL,13,Fparamedics to save his life.
OL,15,FEmergency services were called at
OL,16,Faround 11pm after gunshots were heard.
OL,18,FPolice said CCTV showed a suspect, who
OL,19,Farrived and left on a bike, firing
OL,20,Fseveral shots at the man who was
OL,21,Fsitting in a white Nissan Juke.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
