OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774887078
OL,3,CPolice hunt gunman after man shot dead
OL,4,Cin car near Euston station
OL,6,FHis next of kin have been informed and
OL,7,Fare being supported by specialist
OL,8,Fofficers.
OL,10,FDetective Chief Inspector Joanna
OL,11,FYorke, whose team is leading the
OL,12,Finvestigation, said: "We are aware of
OL,13,Fthe concern that this will cause for
OL,14,Fthe local community, and want to
OL,15,Freassure them that we are working hard
OL,16,Fto identify the attacker and bring
OL,17,Fthem to justice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
