OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774887078
OL,3,CPolice hunt gunman after man shot dead
OL,4,Cin car near Euston station
OL,6,F"If anyone has any information that
OL,7,Fcould help us, it is extremely
OL,8,Fimportant that they contact the police
OL,9,F` either through 101, online or via
OL,10,Findependent charity Crimestoppers to
OL,11,Fremain anonymous.
OL,13,F"Our thoughts are with the young man's
OL,14,Ffamily at this incredibly difficult
OL,15,Ftime."
OL,17,FAnyone with information should call
OL,18,F101 quoting CAD 8032/28Mar, or, to
OL,19,Fremain anonymous, Crimestoppers on
OL,20,F0800 555 111.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
